    <text x="470" y="190" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" style="fill:rgb(93, 202, 165);stroke:none;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:&quot;Anthropic Sans&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:middle;dominant-baseline:central">Interprets G-code commands</text>
